snippet.textDisplay: Its really nice to hear the Shillong choir after awhile in general💟. Why the song felt ended so fast? Please make longer versions of around 6-8mins. Both Oh maria song and Maria pita che are known popular songs and inclusion of both together is nice, BUT would have loved if this was ALL NEW ORIGINAL SONG AND NO REMADE/REMIX type songs,was expecting completely new song from platforms like Coke Studio or else there are many platforms which are for Mixtapes.Also, Felt a quite a RUSH with the part of 'Oh Maria' song , seemed little ODD like running too fast. Would have like it more if the composition gave time to breathe within and sink in.   Also, just an observation, almost all coke studio songs this season are kind of rushing to finish- which is missing to create songs that will sink in for years actually. The composition felt running too fast to enjoy fully, THOUGH enjoyed it in places specially that of Shillong Choir- they are always so lovely❤❤. Much love, hope make more good songs that will be remembered for times to come, want those kind of compositions and SLOWER ONES WITH NO RUNNING TOO FAST🤍🤍
